sql:
SELECT DISTINCT players.player_name
FROM players
INNER JOIN awards ON players.player_id = awards.player_id;

external_knowledge:
- "Crown jewel" metaphorically refers to the school with the most awards;
- "Realm of accolades" signifies the domain or context of awards and honors;
- "Laurels" are a metaphor for awards or achievements.

